  "text": "It will be more convenient to describe this result in terms of Arveson's definition of a decomposable product system [CITATION_1] , which we present next for the convenience of the reader. It is worth mentioning that Arveson showed that a product system is decomposable if and only if it is type I. This difficult theorem is the main result, and motivation, for [CITATION_2] .",
